HEADWORD: Ramshackle
<hw>Ram"shac*kle</hw> <pr>(r⟦acr⟧m"sh⟦acr⟧k*k'l)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[Etymol. uncertain.]</ety> <def>Loose; disjointed; falling to
